        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4153",
        "content": "A STREAM CLEVERLY CROSSED.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4153_61735_000003_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4153/61735/4153_61735_000003_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4153",
        "content": "The sagittary correspondence could not last for long.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4153_61735_000003_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4153/61735/4153_61735_000003_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4153",
        "content": "They are but lukewarm lovers who can content themselves with a dialogue carried on at bowshot distance.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4153_61735_000003_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4153/61735/4153_61735_000003_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4153",
        "content": "Hearts brimful of passion must beat and burn together-in close proximity-each feeling the pulsation of the other. \"If there be an Elysium on earth, it is this!\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4153_61735_000004_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4153/61735/4153_61735_000004_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4153",
        "content": "Maurice Gerald was not the man-nor Louise Poindexter the woman-to shun such a consummation.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4153_61735_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4153/61735/4153_61735_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4153",
        "content": "Twice had they stood together in that garden grove-twice had they exchanged love vows-under the steel grey light of the stars; and a third interview had been arranged between them.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4153_61735_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4153/61735/4153_61735_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4153",
        "content": "Little suspected the proud planter-perhaps prouder of his daughter than anything else he possessed-that she was daily engaged in an act of rebellion-the wildest against which parental authority may pronounce itself.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4153_61735_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4153/61735/4153_61735_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4153",
        "content": "His own daughter-his only daughter-of the best blood of Southern aristocracy; beautiful, accomplished, everything to secure him a splendid alliance-holding nightly assignation with a horse hunter!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4153_61735_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4153/61735/4153_61735_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4153",
        "content": "Could he have but dreamt it when slumbering upon his soft couch, the dream would have startled him from his sleep like the call of the eternal trumpet!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4153_61735_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4153/61735/4153_61735_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4153",
        "content": "He had no suspicion-not the slightest.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4153_61735_000010_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4153/61735/4153_61735_000010_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4153",
        "content": "Its very monstrosity would have disarmed him, had the thought been suggested.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4153_61735_000011_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4153/61735/4153_61735_000011_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4153",
        "content": "He could well concede so much to her caprice: since her staying at home could be no disadvantage to the cause that had prompted him to the stern counsel.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4153_61735_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4153/61735/4153_61735_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4153",
        "content": "Her ready obedience had almost influenced him to regret the prohibition. Walking in confidence by day, and sleeping in security by night, he fancied, it might be recalled.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4153_61735_000017_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4153/61735/4153_61735_000017_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4153",
        "content": "It is already known, that this road passed the hacienda of Casa del Corvo, at some distance from the house, and on the opposite side of the river.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4153_61735_000017_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4153/61735/4153_61735_000017_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4153",
        "content": "It is also known that at the same place it traversed a stretch of open prairie, with only a piece of copsewood midway between two extensive tracts of chapparal.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4153_61735_000019_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4153/61735/4153_61735_000019_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4153",
        "content": "On reaching the copse he dismounted; led his horse in among the underwood; \"hitched\" him, by looping his bridle rein around the topmost twigs of an elastic bough; then detaching a long rope of twisted horsehair from the \"horn\" of his saddle, and inserting his arm into its coil, he glided out to the edge of the \"island,\" on that side that lay towards the hacienda.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4153_61735_000020_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4153/61735/4153_61735_000020_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4153",
        "content": "It was a glance of inquiry, ending in a look of chagrin, with some muttered phrases that rendered it more emphatic.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4153_61735_000021_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4153/61735/4153_61735_000021_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4153",
        "content": "\"No use waiting for that beauty to go to bed?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4153_61735_000022_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4153/61735/4153_61735_000022_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4153",
        "content": "The droll conceit, which has so oft amused the nocturnal inebriate of great cities, appeared to produce a like affect upon the night patroller of the prairie; and for a moment the shadow, late darkening his brow, disappeared.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4153_61735_000022_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4153/61735/4153_61735_000022_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4153",
        "content": "If he be abroad there's a good chance of his seeing me on the open ground; not that I should care a straw, if it were only myself to be compromised.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4153_61735_000022_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4153/61735/4153_61735_000022_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4153",
        "content": "By Saint Patrick, I see no alternative but risk it!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4153_61735_000022_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4153/61735/4153_61735_000022_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4153",
        "content": "She don't go down for hours; and there's not the sign of a cloud.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4153_61735_000022_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4153/61735/4153_61735_000022_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4153",
        "content": "No; I must chance it in the clear light.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4153_61735_000022_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4153/61735/4153_61735_000022_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4153",
        "content": "Here goes?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4153_61735_000023_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4153/61735/4153_61735_000023_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4153",
        "content": "Saying this, with a swift but stealthy step, the dismounted horseman glided across the treeless tract, and soon readied the escarpment of the cliff, that formed the second height of land rising above the channel of the Leona.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4153_61735_000024_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4153/61735/4153_61735_000024_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4153",
        "content": "He did not stay ten seconds in this conspicuous situation; but by a path that zigzagged down the bluff-and with which he appeared familiar-he descended to the river \"bottom.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4153_61735_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4153/61735/4153_61735_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4153",
        "content": "In an instant after he stood upon the bank; at the convexity of the river's bend, and directly opposite the spot where a skiff was moored, under the sombre shadow of a gigantic cotton tree.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4153_61735_000026_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4153/61735/4153_61735_000026_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4153",
        "content": "For a short while he stood gazing across the stream, with a glance that told of scrutiny.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4153_61735_000027_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4153/61735/4153_61735_000027_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4153",
        "content": "Becoming satisfied that no one was there, he raised the loop end of his lazo-for it was this he carried over his arm-and giving it half a dozen whirls in the air, cast it across the stream.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4153_61735_000028_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4153/61735/4153_61735_000028_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4153",
        "content": "The noose settled over the cutwater of the skiff; and closing around the stem, enabled him to tow the tiny craft to the side on which he stood.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4153_61735_000030_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4153/61735/4153_61735_000030_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4153",
        "content": "Leaping out, he secured it as it had been before, against the drift of the current; and then, taking stand under the shadow of the cotton tree, he appeared to await either a signal, or the appearance of some one, expected by appointment.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    }
]